75
00:03:06,199 --> 00:03:07,800
I promise

76
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,840
to give you the best of everything.

77
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,840
That's really not necessary.

78
00:03:13,599 --> 00:03:14,599
Xiao Yuan Yuan,

79
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,400
then

80
00:03:16,919 --> 00:03:17,800
rest early.

81
00:03:21,479 --> 00:03:22,840
Escaped trouble again.

82
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,800
