103
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,439
Why are you here?

104
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:05,919
I just told Xiao Tao

105
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:07,520
I'd visit you when I have time.

106
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,759
Yes, Du Momo,

107
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:10,840
Gongzhu often says she wants to visit you.

108
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:13,479
Gongzhu's words humble me.

109
00:04:13,759 --> 00:04:15,759
