125
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,519
Let me see them.

126
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:49,360
See if they serve you well.

127
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:51,160
Alright.

128
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,040
Du Momo

129
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,680
We'll go together later.

130
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,920
Yes.

131
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:01,600
This—

132
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,759
