142
00:05:19,319 --> 00:05:20,439
that you must obey your master?

143
00:05:20,439 --> 00:05:21,519
I don't need it. Take it away.

144
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:22,920
Yes.

145
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,759
Young Master Xie, come with me quickly.

146
00:05:31,759 --> 00:05:33,079
Gongzhu asked you to go learn etiquette.

147
00:05:34,399 --> 00:05:36,319
Even the study companion must learn etiquette?

148
00:05:36,759 --> 00:05:37,759
You'll know once you go.

149
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,079
Gongzhu, Young Master Xie is here.

150
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:48,439
You are

151
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:49,680
Xie Yuan.

152
00:05:51,519 --> 00:05:52,720
You see Gongzhu,

153
00:05:53,199 --> 00:05:54,279
