192
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,360
You—

193
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,600
You—

194
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:20,040
How dare you, how dare—

195
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:20,680
How dare you!

196
00:07:25,639 --> 00:07:26,560
